    <span class="post-cat">Software Review · AI Writing</span>
    <h1>Wordtune Review 2026: $9.99/mo AI Rewriter — Worth It After Testing?</h1>
    <p class="description">Wordtune is the best sentence-level AI rewriter on the market, used by 10M+ writers to rephrase, adjust tone, and tighten clarity. It also <strong>does not write a full article, does not research keywords, and does not publish anywhere</strong>. After 30 days inside the free, Plus, Unlimited, and Business tiers — plus interviews with 8 paying customers — here is the honest 2026 verdict.</p>
