            <div class="cc-row"><span>Ahrefs or Semrush (keyword data)</span><strong>$129</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Surfer or Frase (content scoring)</span><strong>$119</strong></div>
            <div class="cc-row"><span>Writers — articles @ $100 each</span><strong>$3,000</strong></div>
