            <p>Want the full content pipeline without the stack? Let's see if your site qualifies.</p>
            <a href="/demo/">Get my free audit →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ Wordtune is not an SEO tool</div>
          <p>Buying Wordtune to improve SEO is like buying a Sharpie to write a book. It is a useful tool. It is not the job. SEO needs keyword research, content production, on-page optimisation, and publishing — Wordtune does none of those.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta dark">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Need full SEO articles, not sentence rewrites?</h4>
            <p>We'll audit your site and show you exactly what would generate the highest ROI for <strong>your</strong> business — DIY tool stack, agency, or done-for-you platform.</p>
