        <h2 id="pros-cons">Pros and cons after 30 days</h2>

        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros-card">
            <h4>✓ What Wordtune gets right</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Rewrite suggestions are the best in the category</li>
              <li>Chrome extension works inside Docs, Gmail, LinkedIn, Notion</li>
              <li>Free plan is genuinely usable (10 rewrites/day)</li>
              <li>Tone control is smooth and predictable</li>
              <li>Spices feature inserts examples and analogies inline</li>
              <li>Summariser handles PDFs and long articles well</li>
              <li>Microsoft Word add-in for enterprise users</li>
              <li>iOS and Android apps for on-the-go editing</li>
              <li>Predictable, transparent pricing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="cons-card">
            <h4>✗ Where Wordtune hurts</h4>
            <ul>
