              <li>No keyword research, no SEO optimisation, no SERP analysis</li>
              <li>AI Assist quality lags GPT-4 and Claude</li>
              <li>Spices statistics need fact-checking every time</li>
              <li>Expand adds fluff more often than it adds value</li>
              <li>AI21 Labs reduced active development in 2025</li>
              <li>Per-user Business pricing scales for teams</li>
              <li>No content collaboration features (it is a single-writer tool)</li>
              <li>Free plan cap is hit quickly during real work</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Need a full SEO content engine — not a sentence rewriter?</h4>
            <p>theStacc writes, optimises, and publishes 30 SEO articles per month to your CMS. <strong>Try it for $1</strong>, cancel anytime.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/checkout/" class="cta-btn-inline">Start $1 trial <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No annual contract</span>
          </div>
