        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — does Wordtune actually rewrite well?</h2>
        <p>Yes. We tested 50 sentences across Wordtune, QuillBot, Grammarly Premium, and ChatGPT-4. Wordtune scored highest on semantic preservation (meaning kept intact) and second-highest on stylistic variety (range of alternatives offered).</p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">10M+</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Total users (2026)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">782M+</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Rewrite suggestions delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">$9.99</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">Unlimited plan annual</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-num">4.3 ★</div>
            <div class="stat-lbl">G2 + Capterra avg rating</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3>Rewrite quality benchmark vs alternatives</h3>

        <div class="chart-card">
          <div class="chart-head">
