        <h2 id="verdict">Is Wordtune worth it in 2026? Final verdict</h2>
        <p><strong>For writers who already write a lot: yes.</strong> $6.99/mo for unlimited sentence rewrites is fair value if you write 10+ hours a week. The Chrome extension is the daily-driver feature.</p>

        <p><strong>For non-native English writers: yes.</strong> Wordtune's tone control and rephrase quality is meaningfully better than free alternatives. Worth the price for clarity polish alone.</p>

